Noughts and Crosses

Noughts and Crosses, also known as a TicTacToe or Xs and Os, is a popular board game for 2 players.

Installation

Standalone executables are available and tested for Windows 10 and Linux(Ubuntu 18.04) systems. Please download the game using Windows or Linux version.

Status

In development. Please see issues.

Features

  • currently only one mode: Player vs Computer
  • randomly assign player to X or O
  • first turn is X
  • one difficulty level - easy (AI randomly places X or O)
